window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Bunny girls make everything better.</b></p> <p>So far, this has proven to be an absolute truth to Hunter.</p> <p>Stranded in an alternate version of Earth with most of his memories gone, the super soldier has been doing whatever it takes to protect his new mates, help whatever refugees they find in the process, and get them all to safety.</p> <p>At last they've arrived at the fabled Warren: a secret, high-tech survival shelter. Except there's been some complications. The Warren is empty, and new threats have risen. As the wolves and the tigers fight over the fleeing rabbits, mysterious entities known as Trinkets wage war on everyone with terrifying consequences. And that's to say nothing of the worsening weather and lack of resources.</p> <p>Hunter's going to have to work harder than he ever has if he's going to keep his pregnant mates safe and stop it all from falling apart.</p> <p><i>Down the Rabbit Hole Collection Two</i> collects the next four episodes of the series, and includes two bonus short stories that take place from the girls' perspective.</p>"; 
